Package jsymbolic2.commandline

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CommandLineArgs
    Allows jSymbolic's functionality to be accessed from the command line.
    CommandLineConfig
    Running jSymbolic from the command line using a configuration file.
    CommandLineFeatureExtraction
    A general class that deals with the feature extraction process to be used from the command line.
    CommandLineUtils
    Common utilities that can be used throughout the jSymbolic software.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    CommandLineSwitchEnum
    Deals with the command line switches and how to parse and direct the appropriate action.
